## Items up for discussion

### Officer elections

Michael Schultheiss, Stephen Frost, and Héctor Orón Martínez expressed interest
in continuing their respective positions as President, Vice-President, and
Treasurer. Tim Potter has resigned from the Board.

There were no other candidates for the seats of President, Vice-President, or
Treasurer. Voting to close nominations commenced:

<table>
  <tr><td>Joe Conway</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Forrest Fleming</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Stephen Frost</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
