  <tr><td>Jeremy Stanley</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Zach van Rijn</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
</table>

Vote passed with 9 yes, 0 no and 0 abstain. Michael Schultheiss is elected
President, Stephen Frost is elected Vice-President, and Héctor Orón Martínez is
elected Treasurer.

Both Forrest Fleming and Zach van Rijn expressed interest in the Secretary position. Vote commenced:

